      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BYE BYE TAIPAN (3) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing third and beaten one length (20.06) behind Mrs. Eshay at this track. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Rates highly and will give a great sight. QUEST FOR PACE (1) struggled for best form latest, finishing 4th (25.73) in a Mix 5 at Q Lakeside. Form here at this distance is strong including four wins. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. One of the main contenders. MR FRESH (8) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 366m (20.09). Form here at the trip sound including nine wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can do much better this time. CURIOUS CAZA (2) was in the money last start at big odds - poses a threat again.",
